## 🛠️ Technology Stack

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│              COMPLETE TECHNOLOGY STACK                   │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

DATA LAYER:
├─ Yahoo Finance API (yfinance) - Stock prices
├─ News API - Market sentiment data
├─ SQLite Database - Historical data storage
└─ Python Requests Library - API integration

ANALYSIS LAYER:
├─ Pandas - Data manipulation and analysis
├─ NumPy - Numerical computations
├─ Scikit-learn - Machine learning models
├─ TextBlob - Natural language processing
└─ Custom Python Scripts - Technical indicators

AUTOMATION LAYER:
├─ Make.com - Workflow orchestration
├─ Google Sheets API - Data logging
├─ Slack API - Real-time alerts
├─ SMTP Email - Daily reports
└─ Scheduled Execution - Cron jobs

VISUALIZATION LAYER:
├─ Power BI - Interactive dashboards
├─ Matplotlib - Statistical charts
├─ Seaborn - Data visualization
└─ Google Sheets - Live data display

LANGUAGES & FRAMEWORKS:
├─ Python 3.8+ - Core analysis engine
├─ SQL - Database queries
├─ JSON - Data interchange
└─ Markdown - Documentation

DEPLOYMENT:
├─ SQLite - Lightweight database
├─ Cloud Scheduler - Automated execution
└─ Git/GitHub - Version control
```

