## 🚀 Quick Start Guide

### Prerequisites
- Python 3.8 or higher
- pip (Python package manager)
- Make.com account (free)
- Google Sheets (free)
- Slack (free)

### Installation

```bash
# 1. Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/YOUR-USERNAME/stock-alert-automation.git
cd stock-alert-automation

# 2. Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# 3. Run the analysis
python stock_analysis.py

# 4. View results
cat stock_analysis_results.json
```

### Expected Output

