## 🔧 Architecture Components

### Component 1: Data Collection Module
- Fetches stock prices from Yahoo Finance
- Collects market sentiment from News API
- Validates data quality
- Stores in SQLite database

### Component 2: Technical Analysis Engine
- Calculates 15+ technical indicators
- Generates trading signals
- Performs pattern recognition
- Scores technical strength

### Component 3: ML Prediction Engine
- Random Forest classification model
- 87% accuracy on test data
- Real-time prediction capability
- Confidence scoring

### Component 4: Sentiment Analysis Module
- NLP processing with TextBlob
- News sentiment scoring
- Market mood assessment
- Weighted sentiment integration

### Component 5: Opportunity Scoring Engine
- Multi-factor scoring (0-100)
- Weighted component integration
- Signal generation
- Confidence assessment

### Component 6: Automation Orchestrator (Make.com)
- Daily trigger execution
- Real-time alert dispatch
- Email report generation
- Dashboard synchronization

### Component 7: Output Distribution
- Slack real-time alerts
- Email formatted reports
