## 📊 Database Schema

```
Tables:
├─ stocks (5 records)
│  ├─ stock_id (PK)
│  ├─ symbol (AAPL, MSFT, etc.)
│  └─ company_name
│
├─ daily_prices (1,260+ records)
│  ├─ price_id (PK)
│  ├─ stock_id (FK)
│  ├─ price_date
│  ├─ open_price, high_price, low_price, close_price
│  └─ volume
│
├─ technical_indicators (252+ records)
│  ├─ indicator_id (PK)
│  ├─ stock_id (FK)
│  ├─ analysis_date
│  ├─ ma_20, ma_50, ma_200
│  ├─ rsi, macd, signal_line
│  └─ bollinger_bands
│
├─ signals (156+ records)
│  ├─ signal_id (PK)
│  ├─ stock_id (FK)
│  ├─ signal_date
│  ├─ signal_type (BUY/SELL/HOLD)
│  ├─ confidence_score
│  └─ result (WIN/LOSS/PENDING)
│
├─ sentiment_analysis (252+ records)
│  ├─ sentiment_id (PK)
│  ├─ stock_id (FK)
│  ├─ analysis_date
│  ├─ sentiment_score (-1.0 to 1.0)
│  └─ summary
│
├─ predictions (252+ records)
│  ├─ prediction_id (PK)
│  ├─ stock_id (FK)
│  ├─ prediction_date
│  ├─ predicted_close
│  ├─ model_accuracy
│  └─ verified_at
│
├─ opportunity_scores (252+ records)
│  ├─ score_id (PK)
│  ├─ stock_id (FK)
│  ├─ score_date
│  ├─ overall_score (0-100)
│  └─ recommendation
│
└─ alerts_log (1,000+ records)
   ├─ alert_id (PK)
   ├─ signal_id (FK)
   ├─ alert_type (SLACK/EMAIL/SMS)
   ├─ status (SENT/DELIVERED/FAILED)
   └─ timestamp

Indexes: 10+ for optimal query performance
Views: 8 for common analysis patterns
Queries: 20+ for comprehensive analytics
```

